Yesuꞌu kim dowal mo kïgïna akasïblïkake:<TS3>(<a href="tw://bible.*?40.4.1-11">Mat 4:1-11</a>, <a href="tw://bible.*?41.1.12-13">Mrk 1:12-13</a>)Yesus in kim Yordan kon lwahal zaka, Alap mo Enhona dekam mes bi gweblaka. Dekam zep zi srëm lang san dep zersong gweka.
