Yesuꞌu kim nër dwanukke:<TS3>(<a href="tw://bible.*?40.27.57-61">Mat 27:57-61</a>, <a href="tw://bible.*?41.15.42-47">Mrk 15:42-47</a>, <a href="tw://bible.*?43.19.38-42">Yoh 19:38-42</a>)<sup>(50-51)</sup> Yahudi mo aha ëna Arimatea walya Yusup, zen zini dawem tanganna, hen zini man desa blikip neisïk gweblak. Zen man tangan Alap de kïtak nabakam ïrïk gïlzïn hap hohle gweꞌanka. Zen sap Yahudi mo teipsïn sinodenak de aha mamna, hwëna zen hom Yesuꞌu de tan hap de ol aha-en gunnuk ola mas gulku.
