Yaklana in Jumatkam, hen man kam-en gweꞌak, zep Hari Sabatnak dikim hatan hap aha-ere jam maekam hom lwaꞌak.<RF q=+>Yahudi mo Hari Sabatna, Jumat mo yakla dum gwehen nakon naït gwibik, hëndep Sabtu mo yakla dum gwe hennak zausuk gwek.
