Hwëna man tïtï laka, “Bahem tamaran. Aban mae neik truwek. Angkam man kawen hap golek de gweꞌan.” Zao zep ki hëndep seweka.
Kim tembane hap teinikin anek, Yesus ki zep rotina gul ineka, ki zep Alap hap rotina in hap dawemna golblaka. Ki zep ahap gul guku, dekam zep zëbe nikhip dena teisyazimki.
Hëndep dekam zep zëno nik mo nwena hleng neizimk, “O an Yesus suke!” Hwëna Zen dekam zep zëno nik mo nwe nakon aya gweka.
