Zi darena in ki zep hen aïsïl eibiridaꞌanka– men kirekam oranak zëbon nebon joweka, hen roti kwa-kwak gunnuk kim anakan tame laka, “An Yesus suke!”
Yesus kim aumwa hap de ol zïm-zïmnï golzimkike:<TS3>(<a href="tw://bible.*?40.28.16-20">Mat 28:16-20</a>, <a href="tw://bible.*?41.16.14-18">Mrk 16:14-18</a>, <a href="tw://bible.*?43.20.19-23">Yoh 20:19-23</a>, <a href="tw://bible.*?44.1.6-8">Kis 1:6-8</a>)Zen kim nama kirekam lonbiridaꞌanka, dekam zep Yesus Zëna zëno mae mo ngïrïnnïk etan jowe zaka. Zao zep gubiridaka, “Dawem. Em Alap mo taha terenake lowe heꞌan.”
Ki zep auna ëhlok hen ëaïrïꞌak. Man tim dik, “An zi au!”
