Sap menkam zi darena in hom tame ulki, hwëna kim iwe lïlkï, zen dekam zep dam ulsuku– mensa Alap mo hamal hap de olak zëbe hap dena anakan lwakye, “Zen tïn nïkon sa ngaya gwera.”
Zen dekam zep gol san dep ola halka.
Yesus kim Zënaka Magdala wenya Maria hap zertreibirkike:<TS3>(<a href="tw://bible.*?40.28.9-10">Mat 28:9-10</a>, <a href="tw://bible.*?41.16.9-11">Mrk 16:9-11</a>)Hwëna Magdala wenya Maria nama kaso hulak iwe ë nakon gwëꞌak, hen gosa kon gwëꞌak. Zen ki zep go gwën naban huwehek– kaso mwa san dikim ake irin hip.
Hwëna dekam zep Alap mo dam taha nakore zi darena zë akeink. Zëno nik mo pakeanna ngap-ngapna. Men zëwe Yesus mo tokna nënnek, zao inikinꞌinka– ahana men desan nola kim nën nekke, ahana tana san dekam.
Zen dekam zep lakensibirki, “Em ba habe gona gwëꞌara?”Dekam zep ding gulzimk, “Ano Bian mo tok naka nërhak, hen ëe homë tame guꞌun, ‘Endawe mes yap nënnek?’”
Kirekam kim guzimk, zëna ki zep tahan san lero gwek. Dekam zep hwëna Yesuꞌu hla tak. Zen hwëna hom anakan tame tak, “An Yesus.”
